        <message_html><![CDATA[<div style="caret-color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard; text-size-adjust: auto;">
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: yellow;"><img style="align: top;" title="" src="HR%20Mail%20Logo.pngx" alt="HR Email Logo" align="top" border="" hspace="" vspace="" /></span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: yellow;">CONFIDENTIAL. THIS SHOULD NOT BE SHARED WITH THE CANDIDATE</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt; background-color: yellow;">!<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOWEVER, YOU MAY HAVE THE CANDIDATE CONTACT HR FOR FURTHER INFORMATION.</span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Note this is an automated communication being sent by Human Resources.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">The following candidate is currently in the Pre-Adverse Notification stage of the Background Investigation Review process.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Candidate:</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span class="Apple-converted-space"> ${request_number.first_name_of_candidate} ${request_number.last_name_of_candidate}</span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Position Applied</span><span style="font-size: 10pt;">: </span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">${request_number.position_applied}</span><br /></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Hiring Manager:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span class="Apple-converted-space">${request_number.hiring_manager}</span></span><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span class="Apple-converted-space"><br /></span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">The candidate has been sent instructions via USPS mail that requires a response within five (5) days.&nbsp; In the event a response is received, the response will be reviewed to determine the next steps and/or the candidate will be referred to the<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong>Background Investigation Committee (BIC)</strong><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>for further review.&nbsp;<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="color: red;">Until a decision is made the Candidate is not authorized to work.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">The BIC meets two times per week, normally on Wednesday and Friday. Referral to the BIC does not necessarily indicate that the candidacy of the applicant will be impacted, referral is for the purpose of determining eligibility and suitability for hire based on factors such as the Background Investigation results and position description.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">What Must I Do As the Hiring Manager?</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Take a moment to review the references that you checked during the interview process. Encourage the Candidate to contact HR and to thoroughly review the USG Background Investigation Policy prior to and during candidacy. You may also use this opportunity to refresh your memory of the USG Background Investigation Policy as well.&nbsp; The link is below for your convenience.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Background Investigation Committee (BIC):<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">the<strong><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>BIC<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></strong>is charged with determining and reviewing questions of suitability of hire when the background results appear to be inconsistent with BOR policy. All information is and must be kept confidential.</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Background Investigation:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">An investigation may be comprised of, but not limited to, one or more of the following checks:</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-bottom: 0in; caret-color: #000000; font-family: -webkit-standard; text-size-adjust: auto; margin-top: 0in; list-style-position: inside;">
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Criminal History</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Social Security Number/Name Trace</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Federal and State Criminal History Search</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Multi-State Sex Offender Search</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">National Database Watch List Scan</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Academic/Education Credentials</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Credit History</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Motor Vehicle History Search</span></li>
<li style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica-Normal;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Drug &amp; Alcohol Testing</span></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">References</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">:</span></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">University System of Georgia/Board of Regents Background Investigation Policy:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><a style="color: #954f72;" href="http://www.usg.edu/hr/manual/background_investigation">http://www.usg.edu/hr/manual/background_investigation</a></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">If you have any questions, please feel free to contact the undersigned at 678-466-4230 or via email.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: helvetica;">Thank you,&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;">Human Resources</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; caret-color: #000000; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: helvetica;"><strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">o</span></strong><span style="font-size: 10.5pt;">: 678.466.4230&nbsp;|&nbsp;<strong>f</strong>: 678.466.4239</span></span></p>
</div>]]></message_html>
